      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Erik Madsen</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:146px;\"><a href=\"https://www.madchess.net/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/b/bc/ErikMadsen.jpg\" width=\"144\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:ErikMadsen.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Erik Madsen <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Erik Madsen</b>,<br />\nan American professional programmer and application development supervisor specializing in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_SharePoint\">SharePoint</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Workflow\">workflow</a>, and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Service-oriented_architecture\">service oriented architecture</a>.\nAs an advocate of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Visual_Studio\">Visual Studio</a> and <a href=\"/C_sharp\" title=\"C sharp\">C#</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/.NET_Framework\">.NET</a> as well as amateur chess player, Erik is author of <a href=\"/RumbleMinze\" title=\"RumbleMinze\">RumbleMinze</a> and its successor <a href=\"/MadChess\" title=\"MadChess\">MadChess</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, both written in C# and conform to the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">Universal Chess Interface</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2012_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2012 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erik_Madsen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2012_...\">2012 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erik_Madsen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2012 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43491\">RumbleMinze&#160;: A New C# .NET Engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 28, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=485936#485936\">Re: Question About CPP-C#, Performance, and Square Representation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 03, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45723\">MadChess 1.0 Released (C# .NET Engine)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 25, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45795\">Score Inaccuracy: An Engine Weakening Algorithm</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 31, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">Playing Strength</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51973\">MadChess UCI_LimitStrength Algorithm</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 12, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a>, <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">Playing Strength</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54320\">MadChess 2.0 Development</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 12, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erik_Madsen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57920\">MadChess 2.0 Released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 12, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63248\">MadChess 2.1 Released - Supports Windows, Linux, Mac</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 23, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68759\">MadChess 3.0 Beta</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 29, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69035\">Particle Swarm Optimization Code</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 24, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erik_Madsen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68759&amp;start=19\">Re: MadChess 3.0 Beta</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 23, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74931\">Engine Crash Detective Story</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 29, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Debugging\" title=\"Debugging\">Debugging</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erik_Madsen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.madchess.net/\">MadChess – My UCI Chess Engine + My Writings as an Amateur Chess Player</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erik_Madsen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.madchess.net/\">MadChess – My UCI Chess Engine + My Writings as an Amateur Chess Player</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45723\">MadChess 1.0 Released (C# .NET Engine)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erik Madsen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 25, 2012</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228202656\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 55/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 110/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw